# vim-p6doc

vim plugin for perl6 doc `p6doc`.

## Usage

```vim
:P6doc [keyword]
```

## Requirements

perl6, p6doc

## Installation

To install using pathogen.vim:

    cd ~/.vim/bundle
    git clone https://github.com/mattn/vim-p6doc.git
    
To install using [Vundle](https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim):

    " add this line to your .vimrc file
    Plugin 'mattn/p6doc-vim'

